https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pPBQ7xPcc0t6334SUAwZe2iPpsl.jpg Australia’s national game is under threat from all world sports. Now the AFL must find new ways to survive in this global market. AUSSIE RULES THE WORLD follows AFL superstar Brett Kirk on an international mission to save the game. Narrated by award winning actor David Wenham- this film uncovers people’s passion for footy in unexpected corners of the globe. Footy will never be the same! Aussie Rules the World
